    "display_name": "Sepia Filter",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Applying a sepia filter gives a photo a warm, brownish tone that mimics the look of old photographs. This effect is achieved by adjusting the red, green, and blue values of each pixel to emphasize warm colors and soften cooler tones, creating a vintage or nostalgic feel.",
